name: Lana Wolfe
what_you_do: Lana Wolfe is an author, speaker, and life coach who focuses on helping individuals overcome negative self-talk, trauma from relationships, and resistance to success through the Law of Attraction.
who_you_serve: Lana serves individuals seeking personal development and healing, particularly those dealing with negative self-talk, trauma, and a desire for success in manifesting their goals.
current_projects: Upcoming podcast 'Get Off Your Duff with Duff Gardner' and speaking engagement at Harvard University on October 23.
